In addition to the [[harmony:extended object api|extended object api proposal]], ES-Harmony could standardize some useful but missing built-in methods on Object: 

<code javascript>
Object.getPropertyDescriptors(obj) -> pdmap
Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptors(obj) -> pdmap
</code>

The ''pdmap'' type denotes a "property descriptor map", i.e. an object whose keys are property names and whose values are property descriptors for the corresponding properties.
